, 台灣人好nice<br />\n<br />\n有支那團後, 台北 高雄 阿里山 日月潭比狗行<br />\n<br />\n之後有排又少左支那人, 好啲啦終於<br />\n<br />\n而家會揀少支那人嘅地方行下算"},{"pid":"3c66a9772b006527e83f69a368b82d97d424761f","tid":962411,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:28:02.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fc9a82027e01ce7caf9dc460aa229015d59c0a","tid":962411,"uid":117200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:29:01.000Z","msg":"人地個啲就真係旅遊<br />\n香港個班係刷數據走水貨<br />\n問佢中唔中意香港個個都答很討厭"},{"pid":"2fab92612c51d41612f16a5278dcae71d3169d30","tid":962411,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:31:13.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c20b69b3eb2618b5efe7f2084efaa6f4f8926f","tid":962411,"uid":37539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:31:35.000Z","msg":"越南個d 長期居留添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}